King Goodwill Zwelithini with KZN Premier Willies Mchunu, KZN MEC for transport, community safety and liaison Mxolisi Kaunda, KZN MEC for health Dr Sibongiseni Dhlomo, Prince Mangosuthu Buthelezi and House of Traditional Leaders provincial chairperson Phathisizwe Chiliza at the prayer on social ills and killings in the province hosted by the king yesterday. Zwelithini also yesterday called an imbizo of chiefs overseeing tribal land in the province to deal with tribal land issues.